-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----
TODO: replace with your actual Ed25519 public key before publishing.

Generate keys:
  openssl genpkey -algorithm ed25519 -out private.pem
  openssl pkey -in private.pem -pubout -out public_key.pem

Store the base64-encoded private key as SIGNING_KEY in GitHub Actions secrets:
  base64 -w 0 private.pem

Copy the 32-byte hex public key into updater/updater.go (const publicKey).
-----END PUBLIC KEY-----
